text.tspan: Average years of schooling vs. expected years of schooling, 2021
The average number of years the population older than 25 participated in formal education. The expected years of
schooling is the number of years a child of school entrance age can expect to receive if the current age-specific
enrollment rates persist throughout the child’s schooling.
